{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781420731350,"sessionID":"ses_13b0d8207ffeDxrpg470blid9T","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_HbZDa2iqmZDFh4QVpjv2cScg","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-research agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-research/SKILL.md and execute the research loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/006-competitor-design-tools-research\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/006-competitor-design-tools-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55fast-1781420686076-jgor8g\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: research\n  config.maxIterations: 5\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/006-competitor-design-tools-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/006-competitor-design-tools-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast. Do not touch any path outside /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/006-competitor-design-tools-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55fast","specFolder":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/006-competitor-design-tools-research","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":false},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"No matching trigger phrases found\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"count\": 0,\n    \"results\": [],\n    \"matchType\": \"trigger-phrase\",\n    \"degradedMatching\": null,\n    \"triggerSignals\": [],\n    \"cognitive\": null\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Ensure memories have trigger phrases defined\",\n    \"Try a different prompt or check memory content\",\n    \"[session] Context quality is degraded. Session may benefit from a `session_resume` call.\",\n    \"Auto-surface hook: injected 10 constitutional and 5 triggered memories (73ms)\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 2263,\n    \"latencyMs\": 86,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"autoSurface\": {\n      \"constitutionalCount\": 10,\n      \"triggeredCount\": 5,\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-14T07:05:31.259Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 73\n    },\n    \"autoSurfacedContext\": {\n      \"constitutional\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": 11538,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/verify-before-completion-claims.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Verify Before Completion Claims\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: a positive check whose result you actually read. | Prioritize when: a state that isn't real. (Owner: \\\"Report outcomes faithfully\\\"; \\\"never claim an unverified commit/file.\\\")\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 11537,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec