{"type":"text","timestamp":1781420804905,"sessionID":"ses_13b0d8207ffeDxrpg470blid9T","part":{"id":"prt_ec4f43331001kzw5TKgzMwh2Yj","messageID":"msg_ec4f3ff75001w74V1I5pLHjoZk","sessionID":"ses_13b0d8207ffeDxrpg470blid9T","type":"text","text":"The YAML contains parent-spec write-back and save steps, but this lineage prompt hard-locks writes to the lineage artifact directory and asks only for init, loop, and synthesis. I’ll execute the lineage-local subset and record any skipped parent-spec/save behavior inside the lineage state rather than touching parent paths.","time":{"start":1781420798769,"end":1781420804904},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_00c51a1ec4fd9c1f016a2e52febc44819186dc899c677b491b","phase":"commentary"}}}}
