{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781420940862,"sessionID":"ses_13b0d8207ffeDxrpg470blid9T","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"webfetch","callID":"call_lolUlxwbelObcvjLgMI3AjGd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"url":"https://www.builder.io/c/docs/import-from-figma","format":"markdown","timeout":20},"output":"Builder | Builder Figma Plugin   \n\n [Skip to content](#main-content)\n\n[](/)\n\nPlatformResourcesDocs[Enterprise](/enterprise)[Pricing](/pricing)\n\n[CONTACT SALES](/demo)[START BUILDING](/signup)\n\n  \n\nMenu\n\n⌘K\n\nOverview\n\n[\n\nKey concepts in Publish\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/how-builder-works)[\n\nKey concepts in Fusion\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/key-concepts-fusion)[\n\nHow Builder works\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/how-builder-works-technical)[\n\nLearning paths\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/learning)[\n\nCustomize Builder\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/customizing-builder)[\n\nEnterprise hub\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/enterprise-hub)\n\nGet started\n\n[\n\nGet started with Projects\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/get-started-fusion)[\n\nGet started with Publish\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/get-started-publish)\n\nImport from Figma\n\n[\n\nOverview\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/fusion-import-from-figma-overview)[\n\nBuilder Figma plugin\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/builder-figma-plugin)[\n\nFigma to Projects\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/figma-to-fusion)\n\nFigma to Publish\n\n[\n\nFigma Publish workflow\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/figma-to-publish)[\n\nFigma imports Preview URL\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/figma-imports-preview-url)[\n\nClassic export modes\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/figma-plugin-modes)\n\n[\n\nSmart export best practices\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/figma-smart-exports-best-practices)[\n\nPrecise mode configuration\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/figma-auto-layout)[\n\nGenerate code with CLI\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/figma-to-code-builder-cli)\n\nBuilder basics\n\n[\n\nProjects overview\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/fusion-projects-overview)[\n\nProjects dashboard\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/projects-dashboard)[\n\nProjects settings\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/fusion-project-settings)\n\nCreate a Project\n\n[\n\nProjects from prompts\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/fusion-pr