gma and Projects\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/design-with-figma-and-fusion)\n\nPublish basics\n\n[\n\nCore concepts\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/101-structure)\n\nVisual editor\n\n[\n\nOverview\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/visual-editor)\n\nVisual Editor AI\n\n[\n\nGenerate content\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/vcp-create-content)[\n\nInstructions and style inspiration\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/vcp-instructions-style)[\n\nAdd interactivity\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/vcp-interactivity)[\n\nConnect data\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/vcp-connect-data)[\n\nCustom instructions\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/ve-ai-custom-instructions)\n\n[\n\nInsert tab\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/insert-tab)[\n\nOptions tab\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/options-tab)[\n\nStyle tab\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/visual-editor-style-tab)[\n\nLayers tab\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/layers-tab)[\n\nData tab\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/visual-editor-data-tab)[\n\nVisual Editor (classic UI)\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/101-visual-editor)[\n\nEntry templates\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/entry-templates)[\n\nLinks\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/links)[\n\nAdd custom fonts\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/how-to-add-custom-fonts)\n\nForms\n\n[\n\nForms basics\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/forms)[\n\nConnect with Zapier\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/zapier)[\n\nKlaviyo with Builder\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/klaviyo-app-template)\n\n[\n\nBlock types\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/block-types)[\n\nChrome extension\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/chrome-extension)\n\nCollaboration tools\n\n[\n\nCollaboration in Publish\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/collaboration)[\n\nHistory\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/history)[\n\nCommenting\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/commenting)\n\nProductivity tools\n\n[\n\nStudio\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/studio)[\n\nCommand palette\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/command-palette)[\n\nKeyboard shortcuts\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/keyboard-shortcuts)[\n\nImport Markdown\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/markdown)[\n\nManage content\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/managing-content)\n\nPublish in-depth\n\n[\n\nFusion for Publish\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/fusion-for-publish)\n\nContent management\n\n[\n\nOrganize content with folders\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/folders)[\n\nPage hierarchy mode\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/page-hierarchy)[\n\nFilter content\n\n\n\n](/c/docs/filtering