docs/code-tab)\n    -   [Data & Users](/docs/databases)\n        -   [Database Management](/docs/database)\n        -   [App Users](/docs/app-users)\n    -   [Flow tab](/docs/flow-tab)\n    -   [Preview](/docs/preview)\n    -   [Publish](/docs/publish)\n    -   [🌐Custom Domain](/docs/playground-custom-domain)\n    -   [Capture Elements](/docs/capture-elements)\n    -   [Copy to Figma](/docs/copy-to-figma)\n    -   [Version History](/docs/version-history)\n    -   [Fonts](/docs/fonts)\n-   [🆕Add Figma Design System](/docs/add-figma-design-system)\n-   [Project Visibility](/docs/project-visibility)\n-   [Integrations](/docs/integrations)\n    -   [Github](/docs/github)\n    -   [Figma](/docs/figma)\n-   [Team Management](/docs/team-management)\n-   [Playground FAQ](/docs/playground-faq)\n-   [Training data and privacy](/docs/training-data-and-privacy)\n\n## Buddy - Figma Design Agent\n\n-   [🤖Buddy – Figma AI Design Agent](/docs/buddy-figma-design-agent)\n\n## Figma plugin\n\n-   [Figma](/docs/run-anima-inside-figma)\n-   [Design Mode: Inspect](/docs/component-code-inspect)\n    -   [Code settings](/docs/1-code-settings)\n    -   [Inspect code](/docs/2-inspect-code-1)\n    -   [Copy code](/docs/3-copy-code-1)\n    -   [Prompt in Playground](/docs/4-open-in-playground-1)\n    -   [Download code](/docs/5-download-selection-1)\n    -   [Breakpoints](/docs/6-breakpoints-1)\n    -   [AI Personalization](/docs/7-ai-personalization-1)\n-   [Dev Mode: Plugin](/docs/dev-mode)\n    -   [Code settings](/docs/1)\n    -   [Inspect code](/docs/2-inspect-code)\n    -   [Copy code](/docs/3-copy-code)\n    -   [Prompt in playground](/docs/4-open-in-playground)\n    -   [Download selection](/docs/5-download-selection)\n    -   [Breakpoints](/docs/6-breakpoints)\n    -   [AI Personalization](/docs/7-ai-personalization)\n-   [Dev Mode: Figma Panels](/docs/figma-panels)\n-   [Design Mode: Websites & Prototypes](/docs/1-full-flows-code)\n    -   [Responsiveness: Breakpoints](/docs/1-responsive-pages)\n    -   [Responsiveness: Auto-Layout](/docs/2-responsiveness-auto-layout)\n    -   [Entrance animation](/docs/2-entrance-animation)\n    -   [Hover effects](/docs/3-hover-effects)\n    -   [Media element](/docs/4-media-element)\n    -   [Text input](/docs/5-text-input)\n    -   [Submit button](/docs/6-submit-button)\n    -   [Embed code](/docs/7-embed-code)\n    -   [Preview](/docs/8-preview)\n    -   [Sync](/docs/10-sync)\n    -   [Get code](/docs/9-get-code)\n    -   [Publish](/docs/11-publish)\n    -   [Custom domain (Legacy Sync Flow)](/docs/13-custom-domain)\n\n## Anima for agents\n\n-   [Anima MCP](/docs/anima-mcp)\n-   [Anima API](/docs/anima-api)\n-   [Anima AI Agent Design Skill](/docs/anima-ai-agent-design-skill)\n\n## Integrations\n\n-   [Tailwind CSS | Figma | VSCode](/docs/tailwind-css)\n-   [MUI (Material-UI) | Figma | VSCode](/docs/mui-material-ui)\n-   [AntD (Ant Design) | Figma | VSCode](/docs/antd-ant-design-anima-for-figma-frontier-in-vscode)\n-   [ShadCN | VSCode](/docs/shadcn-frontier-in-vscode)\n-   [ShadCN | Figma](/docs/shadcn-figma)\n-   [Bootstrap | VSCode](/docs/bootstrap-frontier-in-vscode)\n-   [Chakra UI | VSCode](/docs/chakra-ui-frontier-in-vscode)\n\n## Frontier - VS Code (Legacy)\n\n-   [Getting Started](/docs/getting-started-20)\n-   [Installation and Commands](/docs/1-installation-and-commands)\n-   [Preferences Settings](/docs/preferences-settings)\n-   [Code and Components Analysis](/docs/code-and-components-analysis)\n-   [Component Matching](/docs/component-matching-copy)\n    -   [Matching Override](/docs/matching-override-copy)\n    -   [Code Injection](/docs/code-injection-copy)\n-   [Translate Figma Into Code](/docs/translate-figma-into-code)\n-   [Stay Up-to-date](/docs/stay-up-to-date)\n-   [FAQ](/docs/faq)\n\n## Anima Webapp (legacy)\n\n-   [Anima Webapp](/docs/anima-webapp)\n-   [Teams](/docs/1-anima-teams)\n-   [Projects](/docs/2-anima-projects)\n-   [The new AI Playground](/docs/3-playground)\n-   [Sharing](/docs/4-sharing)\n\nPowered by [](https://readme.com?ref_src=hub&project=animaapp)\n\n1.  Playground\n\n# Getting Started\n\nWelcome to Anima! Let’s cover all the things you need to know to begin exploring the platform.\n\n# \n\nGetting started\n\n[](#getting-started)\n\n> 📘\n> \n> Go from Figma design, text prompt, or website URL to a working web app with editable code in minutes.\n\nTurn designs, prompts, or websites into live web apps.\n\nAnima Playground lets you go from idea to working code in minutes. Whether you're starting with a polished Figma design, a simple text description, or an existing website you want to recreate, you'll end up with editable, production-ready code.\n\n## \n\nAccessing Anima Playground\n\n[](#accessing-anima-playground)\n\nVisit **[dev.animaapp.com](https://dev.animaapp.com)** to get started.\n\n---\n\n## \n\nChoose your starting point\n\n[](#choose-your-starting-point)\n\nPick the path that matches what you have:\n\n[\n\nStarting from Figma\n\nImport your designs and get production-ready code.\n\n\n\n](https://docs.animaapp.com/docs/starting-from-figma)[\n\nStarting from a prompt\n\nDescribe what you want and let Anima build it.\n\n\n\n](https://docs.animaapp.com/docs/starting-from-a-prompt)[\n\nStarting from a URL\n\nClone any website and customize it.\n\n\n\n](https://docs.animaapp.com/docs/starting-from-a-url)\n\n---\n\n## \n\nEdit your project\n\n[](#edit-your-project)\n\nThe Playground is your interactive space to build and iterate.\n\n-   **Use natural language** — Ask for changes in plain English: \"Make the header sticky,\" \"Add a form,\" \"Style this card,\" or \"Create a dark mode.\"\n-   **Edit the code directly** — Every AI action produces clean, editable code. Modify anything while keeping full control.\n-   **Add and rearrange screens** — Build flows by importing more Figma frames or creating new screens from prompts.\n-   **Preview instantly** — Every change updates the live preview so you can validate interactions and UI before publishing.\n\n[Learn more about editing →](./editing.md)\n\n---\n\n## \n\nConnect a backend\n\n[](#connect-a-backend)\n\nMake your app dynamic by connecting data and APIs.\n\n-   **Use Anima's built-in database** — Create tables, define fields, and connect components to real data in minutes. Great for prototypes, internal tools, and lightweight production apps.\n-   **Add user authentication** — Enable sign-in, sign-up, and protected routes. Add email/password and Google authentication to your app.\n\n[Learn more about data management →](./data-management.md)\n\n---\n\n## \n\nPublish your app\n\n[](#publish-your-app)\n\nWhen you're ready to share your work, publish with one click.\n\n-   **Deploy to a custom domain** — Connect your domain and host your app directly from Anima.\n-   **Use the default Anima URL** — Instantly share your prototype or app with your team.\n-   **Export the code** — Download clean React/HTML/Tailwind code or sync it into your existing codebase.\n\nPublishing is instant, and updates apply automatically whenever you republish.\n\n![Publish your app](https://files.readme.io/e0ed52cf8e0da7fbcb9664fb4485457f386773476463b0b67107a8449b20d0e4-Publish1.png)\n\n[Learn more about publishing →](./publishing.md)\n\n---\n\n## \n\nSet your code preferences\n\n[](#set-your-code-preferences)\n\nSet your code preferences by clicking the settings icon next to the tool name. Choose your framework, UI library, language, and styling before you start building.\n\n![Code preferences settings](https://files.readme.io/987dd0e7d579db610fd6c8ebb90694c4d049bee3b9937e5744ba2fd9f19115a7-image.png)\n\n[Learn more about code preferences →](./code-preferences.md)\n\nCopy Page","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"https://docs.animaapp.com/docs/getting-started (text/html; charset=utf-8)","time":{"start":1781420941001,"end":1781420941464}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0c203b1e40e4a805016a2e538c6dd88191b3ca8783ee7174cf"}},"id":"prt_ec4f65ddc0010YMyJkJP2ntSby","sessionID":"ses_13b0d8207ffeDxrpg470blid9T","messageID":"msg_ec4f635cb001zcCC6CugBLaIGI"}}
