{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781420941906,"sessionID":"ses_13b0d8207ffeDxrpg470blid9T","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"webfetch","callID":"call_9oUWuDyMkfh2icrY6mJyAVFg","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"url":"https://help.framer.com/converting-figma-designs-to-framer","format":"markdown","timeout":20},"output":"---\ntitle: \"Framer: Create a professional website, free. No code website builder loved by designers.\"\ndescription: Build a free website with Framer—enjoy full design freedom, powerful CMS, built-in SEO, and real-time collaboration. Create professional, fully custom sites with the no-code builder loved by designers and high-performing teams.\npublished: \"Jun 12, 2026, 10:48 AM UTC\"\n---\n\n[Join us live June 16 10AM PDT for something big](./events/)\n\n# Build better sites, faster\n\nFramer is the site builder trusted by leading startups and Fortune 500 companies. Build fast and scale more easily with an integrated CMS, analytics, localization, and SEO.\n\n[Start for free](https://framer.com/r/signup)\n\n[Start with AI](./ai/)\n\n[Meet our customers](./stories/)\n\n## Create, collaborate, and go live\n\n### [AI](./#feat-ai)\n\nGenerate site layouts and advanced components in seconds with AI, so you can skip the blank canvas and start designing with confidence.\n\n### [Design](./#feat-design)\n\nCraft responsive layouts and bring them to life with smooth effects, interactions, and animations. Build exactly what you imagine, visually.\n\n[Learn more](./design/)\n\n### [CMS](./#feat-cms-2)\n\nManage and update your content effortlessly with a built-in CMS. Keep your site fresh without touching code.\n\n[Learn more](./cms/)\n\n### [Collaborate](./#feat-collab)\n\nWhether you’re collaborating on the canvas or editing copy directly on the page, updates are seamless and handoff-free.\n\n[Learn more](./collaborate/)\n\nWireframer\n\nI created three unique landing pages in dark mode for your modern design startup: a main landing page, a creative-focused page, and a studio showcase page.\n\nLanding Page 1, Landing Page 2, Landing Page 3, 100%, Benjamin, Paul, 100%, Publish, Title, Holo Shader, Slug, holo-shader\n\nframer.com/update/holo-shader\n\nStatus, Live, Date, 16/04/2026, Section, Section description, Image, Tint, 35E2EB, Featured, Content\n\nIntroducing a brand new addition to our Shader library: Holo. A gradient shader that simulates how light splits into rainbows on holographic surfaces. Instead of colors, you control the math that shapes the colors, and the way the shader warps and flows. Holo is now available in the Insert Panel, under Shaders. [Watch the video](https://youtu.be/gvpnmNprxKo) to learn more about how to customize Holo.\n\n### Latest News\n\nView All Posts, Click to edit, Changes are auto-saved, Site saved\n\nCollaborators are notified. Changes will be visible once the project is published.\n\nOpen in Framer\n\nFinish Editing\n\n## Scale without switching tools\n\n###### Analytics & insights\n\nTrack traffic, measure performance, and monitor conversions.\n\n[Learn more](./analytics)\n\nJune 12, 2026, Pageviews, 258,156, Visitors, 85,458\n\n###### A/B Testing & optimization\n\nA/B testing, funnels, and built-in growth insights.\n\n[Learn more](./analytics)\n\n###### SEO & performance\n\nOptimize every page with built-in SEO settings, metadata, and blazing-fast hosting.\n\n[Learn more](./seo/)\n\nGoogle Lighthouse, 0, SEO, 0, Performance, 0, Accessibility\n\n## Powering ambitious teams worldwide\n\n- [“Framer gives us everything we need to move fast. We don’t wait on dev. We don’t compromise on design.” Henry Modisett Head of Design at Perplexity Read more](./stories/perplexity/)\n  \n- [“At FLORA, we care about flow—how ideas move from imagination to interface. Framer gets that. It gives us the speed to iterate, the freedom to explore, and the power to execute.” Ethan Proia Head of Design at FLORA Read more](./stories/flora/)\n  \n- [“Framer gave us full creative freedom. No code limits, no handoffs. We shipped an immersive brand site in days.” Adam Jiwa Partnerships at Metalab Read more](./stories/biograph/)\n  \n- [“With Framer, our designers can ship updates daily. No dev handoff. No staging hassle.” Jelle Prins Co-Founder at Cradle Read more](./stories/cradle/)\n  \n- [“Framer allowed us to ship high-performing, beautifully designed pages at record speed, all while keeping design control in-house.” Radoslav Bali Design Lead at Miro Read more](./stories/miro/)\n  \n\nPerplexity, Flora, Biograph, Cradle, Miro\n\n## Get pro help from handpicked experts\n\n[Get matched](./match/)\n\n[Find an Expert](https://www.framer.com/experts/)\n\n- [View Expert Trueform Switzerland](https://www.framer.com/@trueform/)\n  [View Expert Alex Aperios United Kingdom](https://www.framer.com/@alex-aperios/)\n  [View Expert Analogue Agency Netherlands](https://www.framer.com/@analogueagency/)\n  [View Expert Fabian Albert United States](https://www.framer.com/@fabian-albert/)\n  \n- [View Expert Allsite Studio Germany](https://www.framer.com/@ben-libor/)\n  [View Expert Aerolab United States](https://www.framer.com/@aerolab/)\n  [View Expert Adriano Reis United States](https://www.framer.com/@adrianoreis/)\n  [View Expert Deserve Studio United States](https://www.framer.com/@deservestudio/)\n  \n\n## Launch faster with community resources\n\n[Templates](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/templates/)\n\n[Plugins](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/plugins/)\n\n[Components](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/components/)\n\n- [View Component Image Slider Component Before and after images](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/components/image-slider/)\n  [View Template Milo Template Furniture shop website](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/templates/milo/)\n  [View Plugin Notion Plugin Sync with Notion](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/plugins/notion/)\n  [View Component Hover Zoom Component Zoom and pan on hover](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/components/hover-image-zoom/)\n  [View Template Archer Template Creative portfolio](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/templates/archer/)\n  [View Plugin Workshop Plugin Turn ideas into components](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/plugins/workshop/)\n  \n\n- [View Component Digital Rotary Radio Component Fully functional radio](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/components/digital-rotary-radio/)\n  [View Template Apex Films Template Multimedia portfolio](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/templates/apex-films/)\n  [View Component Flip Card Component Drag to flip cards](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/components/flipcard-component/)\n  [View Component Animated Gradients Component Image reveal effect](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/components/animated-gradient/)\n  [View Plugin JSON Sync Plugin Import & export CMS with JSON](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/plugins/json-sync/)\n  [View Template Baseform Template Modern design portfolio](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/templates/baseform/)\n  \n\n##### Design bold. Launch fast.\n\n[Start for free](https://framer.com/r/signup)\n\n[Start with AI](./wireframer/)\n\n---\n\n## Navigation\n\n- [Log in](https://framer.com/r/login)\n- [Sign up](https://www.framer.com/r/signup/)\n- [Brand Guidelines](./brand)\n- [Enterprise](./enterprise/)\n- [Pricing](./pricing)\n- [Loading status](https://www.framerstatus.com/)\n- [Mac](https://updates.framer.com/electron/darwin/arm64/Framer.zip?_ga=2.113395847.1447313862.1646043056-273660571.1642151053)\n- [Windows](https://updates.framer.com/electron/win32/x64/Framer.exe?_ga=2.113395847.1447313862.1646043056-273660571.1642151053)\n- [AI](./ai/)\n- [Design](./design/)\n- [Publish](./publish/)\n- [Collaborate](./collaborate/)\n- [Convert](./convert/)\n- [CMS](./cms/)\n- [SEO](./seo/)\n- [Hosting](./hosting/)\n- [Performance](./performance/)\n- [Updates](./updates)\n- [Switch](./switch/)\n- [Startups](./startups/)\n- [Agencies](./agencies/)\n- [Figma to HTML](./solutions/figma-to-html/)\n- [Website builder](./solutions/website-builder/)\n- [Portfolio maker](./solutions/portfolio-website/)\n- [Landing pages](./solutions/landing-pages/)\n- [UI/UX design](./solutions/ui-ux-design/)\n- [No-code](./solutions/no-code-website-builder/)\n- [AEM](./compare/framer-vs-adobe-experience-manager)\n- [Sanity](./compare/framer-vs-sanity)\n- [Claude Code](./compare/framer-vs-claude-code)\n- [Squarespace](./compare/framer-vs-squarespace)\n- [WordPress](./compare/framer-vs-wordpress)\n- [Webflow](./compare/framer-vs-webflow)\n- [Lovable](./compare/framer-vs-lovable)\n- [Figma](./compare/framer-vs-figma)\n- [Wix](./compare/framer-vs-wix)\n- [Codex](./compare/framer-vs-codex)\n- [Unbounce](./compare/framer-vs-unbounce)\n- [Contentful](./compare/framer-vs-contentful)\n- [Ceros](./compare/framer-vs-ceros)\n- [Readymag](./compare/framer-vs-readymag)\n- [Marketplace](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/)\n- [Templates](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/templates/)\n- [Components](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/components/)\n- [Plugins](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/plugins/)\n- [Vectors](https://www.framer.com/marketplace/vectors/)\n- [Free domains](./domains/)\n- [AEO scanner New](./aeo)\n- [State of Sites](https://www.framer.com/state-of-sites-2026/)\n- [Case studies](./stories/)\n- [Developers](./developers/)\n- [Newsletter](./newsletter)\n- [Support](./help/)\n- [Contact](./contact/)\n- [Guides](./guides)\n- [Brand](./brand)\n- [Blog](./blog/)\n- [Meetups](./meetups/)\n- [Careers](./careers/)\n- [Security](./legal/security/)\n- [Abuse](mailto:abuse@framer.com)\n- [Media](./brand)\n- [Legal](./legal/terms-of-service/)\n- [Store New](./store)\n- [Trust center](https://app.eu.vanta.com/framer.com/trust/ow67ujg7iav0t6qtd1o6r2)\n- [Experts](./expert/apply/)\n- [Creators](./creators)\n- [Students](./education/students/)\n- [Ambassadors](./education/ambassadors/)\n","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"https://help.framer.com/converting-figma-designs-to-framer (text/markdown; charset